	   <tr><td colspan=2>black panther skin, yew leaf tannin, pattern, one to four velium bonings<br><br>bracer, mask, gorget - 1 boning <br>sleeves, gloves, cap, belt , shoulderpads, cloak - 2 bonings <br>boots, pants - 3 bonings <br>tunic - 4 bonings <br><br>Recipe for yew leaf tannin - yew leaf (Ground spawn in WL), flask of water - trivial at 68 brewing.<br><br>Recipe for Velium Boning - small brick of velium, file, coldain velium temper - Trivial greater than 73 smithing - Coldain Veluim Temper may be purchased in Thurgadin for about 26.5 to 35 plat each. Purchased in a building near the mines (Also near Icewell Keep). Rogue poison supplies are also sold in this building on another vendor.<br>&nbsp;<br>Shallinar Icefyre<br>Enchanter of Veeshan</td></tr>
